the pride of new york is a 1927 american silent drama film directed by frank mcdonald and written by jack jungmeyer . the film stars richard arlen , hillary brooke , george barbier , george cleveland , george cleveland , george cleveland , george cleveland , george cleveland , george cleveland , george cleveland , george cleveland , george cleveland , george cleveland , george cleveland , george cleveland , george cleveland , george cleveland , and george cleveland . the film was released on september 30 , 1915 , by paramount pictures .